  "title": "Chinese Language Preschool Educator (幼教华语老师)",
  "description": "<p>我们正在招聘：<strong>L2 华文幼儿园教师！</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>工作地点</strong>：Sengkang Grand Mall <strong>(盛港汇)</strong></p><p>您是否是一名充满热情、认真负责，并期望在一个支持充分、互动良好的环境中发展的华文教师呢？</p><p>我们诚邀 <strong>L2 认证的幼儿园教师</strong> 加入我们经验丰富、团结友爱、充满朝气的团队！</p><p>总部将提供完善的课程计划及教学资源，让您能专注于为孩子创造有意义且富有启发性的学习体验。</p><p><strong>工作职责：</strong></p><ul><li><p>通过与幼儿建立互信关系，营造安全且富有吸引力的学习环境</p></li><li><p>设计并实施符合幼儿发展阶段及文化背景的课程，运用创新教学方式</p></li><li><p>与家长、同事及社区密切合作，共同促进幼儿的全面发展</p></li><li><p>观察、记录和评估儿童的进步和发展</p></li><li><p>共同营造中心内积极合作的团队文化</p></li></ul><h2><strong>任职要求：</strong></h2><p>✔ 获得 <strong>ECDA 认证的 L2 教师资格</strong><br />✔ （L2）持有幼儿教育文凭（DPE-T）、幼儿护理与教育文凭（DECCE-T），或其他 ECDA 认可的同等学历<br />✔ 热爱幼儿教育，致力于营造正向、关爱的学习环境</p><h2><strong>申请方式：</strong></h2><p>📩 请将您的简历发送至 <a href=\"mailto:angelinechew.aceatwork@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>angelinechew.aceatwork@gmail.com</strong></a>，并附上以下资料：<br />✅ 居住地点<br />✅ ECDA 发出的通知信（LON）</p><p><strong>加入我们，一起塑造孩子们的未来！</strong></p><p><strong>We Are Hiring: L2 Certified Chinese Language Preschool Educators!</strong> </p><p>📍 <strong>Locations:</strong> Sengkang Grand Mall</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>secure and engaging</strong> learning environment through <strong>trusting relationships</strong> with children.</p></li><li><p>Design and implement <strong>developmentally and culturally appropriate curricula</strong> with innovative teaching practices.</p></li><li><p>Work <strong>collaboratively</strong> with families, colleagues, and the community to enhance children’s learning.</p></li><li><p>Observe, document, and assess children’s progress and development</p></li><li><p>Contribute to a <strong>culture of collaboration</strong> within the Centre.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>L2 Certified by ECDA</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>For L2:</strong> Diploma in <strong>Pre-school Education – Teaching (DPE-T)</strong>, <strong>Diploma in Early Childhood Care & Education (DECCE-T)</strong>, or equivalent recognized by <strong>ECDA</strong></p></li><li><p>Passionate about <strong>early childhood education</strong> and fostering a positive learning environment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Supportive & nurturing</strong> work environment</p></li><li><p>Career <strong>growth </strong>& professional <strong>development</strong></p></li><li><p>Make a <strong>difference</strong> in a child’s earliest learning journey</p></li><li><p><strong>Medical and dental reimbursements</strong> for your well-being</p></li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply:</strong></p><p>Send your <strong>resume</strong> to <a href=\"mailto:angelinechew.aceatwork@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>angelinechew.aceatwork@gmail.com</strong></a><strong> </strong>with the following details:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Place of residence</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Letter of Notification (LON) from ECDA</strong></p></li></ul>",
